'''米高·約翰·禮利'''（{{lang-en|'''Michael John Kightly'''}}，{{bd|1986年|1月24日|catidx=Kightly, Michael}}）出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[埃塞克斯郡|埃塞克斯郡]]的[[巴西爾登|巴西爾登]]（Basildon），是一名職業足球員，司職[[中場#翼鋒|翼鋒]]。

禮利於學童時期在[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]受訓，惟未獲晉升機會而加盟家鄉球隊[[Basildon_United_F.C.|巴西爾登聯]]，不久後獲[[绍森德足球俱乐部|修安聯]]接納而首嘗[[英格蘭足球聯賽|聯賽]]滋味，但僅效力兩年便遭放棄。禮利轉投非聯賽隊伍[[格雷斯竞技足球俱乐部|格雷斯]]後開始展露光芒，最終獲[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]的賞識而平步青雲。

== 生平 ==
=== 球會 ===
;早年
禮利於在學時期效力[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]，但最終被放棄，其後轉投在非[[英格蘭足球聯賽|聯賽]]作賽的家鄉球會[[Basildon_United_F.C.|巴西爾登聯]]（Basildon United）。於2003年3月獲[[绍森德足球俱乐部|修安聯]]賞識收歸旗下，在2002/03年球季煞科日作客[[埃克塞特城足球俱乐部|艾斯特城]]，禮利於完場前後補處子登場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/2976523.stm |title=Exeter 1-0 Southend |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-05-03 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307111319/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/2976523.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2003年12月9日[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|英格蘭聯賽錦標]]主場3-0淘汰[[卢顿足球俱乐部|盧頓]]，禮利射入個人首個入球。12月12日禮利簽署首份[[職業|職業]]合約，為期18個月，直到2005年夏季才屆滿<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11716_2283770,00.html |title=Shrimpers teen signs deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2003-12-12 |accessdate=2009-05-18 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309124621/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11716_2283770,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在效力修安聯的三個球季，禮利雖然獲派在所有盃賽上陣，卻只有13場[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|聯賽]]出場機會，僅有兩次正選出戰。2004/05年球季僅獲一次出場後，於2004年10月22日被外借到[[Farnborough_Town_F.C.|費布洛治]]（Farnborough Town）1個月汲取上陣經驗<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/f/farnborough/3945959.stm |title=Farnborough sign Kightly on loan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-10-22 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307190306/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/f/farnborough/3945959.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後再延長多1個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/4039641.stm |title=Kightly extends Farnborough spell |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-11-24 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307074116/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/4039641.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終於2005年1月21日在3個月借用期滿後才返回修安聯<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/4195959.stm |title=Boro keeper is loaned to Southend |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-01-21 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307130813/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/4195959.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間獲派11場上陣。禮利直到球季結束只能坐在後補席沒有出場機會，雖然修安聯透過附加賽來季升級[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]，但時任領隊[[史堤夫·泰臣|史堤夫·泰臣]]（Steve Tilson）卻在這時告訴禮利球隊不再需要他<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/4596331.stm |title=Kightly released by Southend boss |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-05-31 |accessdate=2009-05-19}}</ref>。

;格雷斯
剛升級[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|議會全國聯賽]]的[[格雷斯竞技足球俱乐部|格雷斯]]簽入禮利，2005年10月15日主場5-0大勝[[Scarborough_F.C.|史卡保罗夫]]（Scarborough），禮利射入加盟以來首個入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4322148.stm |title=Grays Athletic 5-0 Scarborough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-10-15 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613212244/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4322148.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。禮利持續有出色的表現，獲球迷票選為12月份「議會全國聯賽每月最佳球員」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/g/grays_athletic/4629272.stm |title=Kightly wins monthly player award |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-01-19 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2015-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529073028/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/g/grays_athletic/4629272.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2006年4月19日次循環作客再對史卡保罗夫，禮利更大演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，協助格雷斯以7-2的紀錄再次淨勝5球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4906922.stm |title=Scarborough 2-7 Grays |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-04-19 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307143440/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4906922.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。格雷斯最終在聯賽取得第3位，可以參加升級附加賽，雖然禮利在準決賽次回合射入一球，但兩回合累計4-5負於[[Halifax_Town_A.F.C.|夏利法斯]]（Halifax Town）被淘汰<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4973008.stm |title=Grays 2-2 Halifax (agg 4-5) |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-05-10 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308193935/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4973008.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。可是格雷斯卻成功晉級[[英格蘭足總錦標|英格蘭足總錦標]]決賽，於5月14日以2-0擊敗[[Woking_F.C.|胡京]]（Woking）蟬聯冠軍<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4770731.stm |title=Grays beat Cards to retain Trophy |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-05-14 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309203558/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4770731.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。禮利作為一名翼鋒球員，在格雷斯的首季合共射入15球。

2006/07年球季禮利繼續留效格雷斯<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/g/grays_athletic/5067684.stm |title=Sestanovich seals switch to Grays |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-06-10 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2006-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061220230011/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/g/grays_athletic/5067684.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，開季連續4場均取得入球，未到11月已有10球斬獲，並獲徵召加入[[英格蘭足球代表丙隊|英格蘭C隊]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/6135498.stm |title=Fairclough names National squad |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-11-10 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307205900/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/6135498.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。禮利出色的表現獲得[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]的垂青，於2006年11月17日以兩個月緊急借用形式加盟<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/6143282.stm |title=Kightly completes move to Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-11-17 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2016-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160426164411/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/6143282.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]重開前先行轉會，因而錯過代表英格蘭C隊上陣的機會<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/6164834.stm |title=Fairclough alters National squad |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-11-20 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304134914/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/6164834.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月2日首次披上狼隊球衣，作客出戰的對手正正是棄用他的母會[[绍森德足球俱乐部|修安聯]]，狼隊以1-0小勝終場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6183496.stm |title=Southend 0-1 Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-12-02 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307044407/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6183496.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。禮利在第二場比賽對[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]即射入加盟後首個入球兼一箭定江山，穩奪聯賽3分<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6164721.stm |title=QPR 0-1 Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-12-16 |accessdate=2009-05-19 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307152410/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6164721.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。拆禮物日聯賽作客對[[德比郡足球俱乐部|打比郡]]，禮利於完場前射入一球成2-0<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6200279.stm |title=Derby 0-2 Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-12-26 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304101532/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6200279.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。禮利在正式轉會狼隊前，為格雷斯效力的18個月在聯賽上陣53場，其中45場為正選，射入24球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/6298073.stm |title=Kightly flying high at Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-30 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2016-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161026223611/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/6298073.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

禮利於2007年7月14日隨同狼隊返回格雷斯進行季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]，是兩間球會作為禮利交易的部分條款，雙方踢成0-0平手，禮利可以正式與格雷斯球迷說再見，並獲得球迷的熱情的款待<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/6902452.stm |title=Grays reception impresses Kightly |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-07-14 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2007-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070821004059/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/6902452.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;狼隊
2007年1月1日轉會窗重開，在借用期間5場入2球的禮利正式投效[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]，簽約兩年半，狼隊只需付給[[格雷斯竞技足球俱乐部|格雷斯]]象徵費用<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/6222413.stm |title=Wolves sign McIndoe and Kightly |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-01 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2018-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825003141/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/6222413.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，據報僅為25,000[[英鎊|英鎊]]，當時禮利在格雷斯只賺取300[[英鎊|英鎊]]週薪，而在簽約前夕，[[曼联足球俱乐部|曼聯]]亦有意收購這名號稱「非聯賽的[[瑞恩·吉格斯|傑斯]]」（''The Ryan Giggs of non-league football''）的球員<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/article77387.ece |title=United target £300-a-week star |publisher=[[太陽報|''The Sun'']] |date=2006-12-30 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2015-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529071842/http://www.thesun.co.uk/sol/homepage/sport/football/article77387.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後禮利表示雖聽聞曼聯曾聯絡格雷斯，但他仍非常樂意效力狼隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/6230803.stm |title=Kightly delight at Wolves signing |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-04 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2017-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915073435/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/6230803.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。禮利在餘下的[[2006年至2007年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|球季]]在狼隊成為常規正選，為球隊再射入多6球，包括在[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|聯賽]]煞科日作客對[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]，禮利射入反超前2-1的一球，最終協助狼隊以4-1獲勝及取得聯賽第5位的成績，可以參加升級附加賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6602859.stm |title=Leicester 1-4 Wolverhampton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-06 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2017-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915072453/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6602859.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。禮利的表現獲得狼隊球迷的認同，在投票狼隊年度最佳球員選舉中，得票僅次於[[門將|門將]][[Matt_Murray_(footballer)|馬特·梅利]]（Matt Murray）獲第二位。狼隊在升級附加賽準決賽兩回合累計2-4不敵同是來自[[黑鄉|黑鄉]]（Black Country）的[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]，無緣升級<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6649727.stm |title=West Brom 1-0 Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-14 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2008-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080516092231/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6649727.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。季後傳聞禮利與多間[[英超|英超]]球會包括[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]、[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查爾頓]]、[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]、[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]及[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]等拉上關係<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/pages/live/articles/sport/football.html?in_article_id=442413&in_page_id=1779 |title=The Screamer...It's the talk of football |publisher=[[每日郵報|''Daily Mail'']] |date=2007-03-15 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2007-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929141219/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/pages/live/articles/sport/football.html?in_article_id=442413&in_page_id=1779 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他於6月18日簽署四年新約平息流言<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/6763641.stm |title=Kightly signs new Wolves contract |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-06-18 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2007-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070824003646/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/6763641.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2007/08年球季]]是禮利加盟後的首個完整球季，2007年8月19日作客3-1擊敗[[谢周三足球俱乐部|錫周三]]，禮利射入本季個人首個入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6941820.stm |title=Sheff Wed 1-3 Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-08-19 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307043519/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/6941820.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；10月24日作客對[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]，禮利梅開二度協助球隊險勝3-2，更升上聯賽榜第三位<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7054154.stm |title=Cardiff 2-3 Wolverhampton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-10-24 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307030949/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7054154.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月25日「黑鄉打吡」作客0-0賽和[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7099752.stm |title=West Brom 0-0 Wolverhampton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-11-25 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307203304/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7099752.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，禮利下半場觸傷[[足踝|足踝]]離場，戴後需要扶柺杖協助步行<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7113611.stm |title=Wolves sweating over injured pair |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-11-26 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307033840/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7113611.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這次受傷使他缺席整個[[聖誕節|聖誕節]]賽期<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7150415.stm |title=Kightly could face Christmas out |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-12-18 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307191127/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7150415.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他於2008年1月初恢復操練<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7165752.stm |title=Kightly nears first-team return |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-12-31 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310125300/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7165752.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1月5日在[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]第三圈對[[剑桥联足球俱乐部|剑桥联]]後補入替踢了30分鐘，射入一球及交出一個助攻，協助狼隊2-1獲勝過關<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7163992.stm |title=Wolves 2-1 Cambridge Utd |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-05 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2020-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928034040/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7163992.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。賽後足踝傷患復發，再次缺席兩場聯賽，狼隊自禮利受傷缺陣的9場聯賽只嘗1勝<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7202829.stm |title=Kightly close to Wolves comeback |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-22 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307041629/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7202829.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1月24日足總盃第四圈作客4-1擊敗[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]，禮利於完場前後補上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7197724.stm |title=Watford 1-4 Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-26 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807215451/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/fa_cup/7197724.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。賽後週日復操僅20分鐘，足踝再次感到痛楚<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7213455.stm |title=Kightly suffers fresh ankle woe |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-28 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160903170106/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7213455.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終於2月29日接受[[手術|手術]]希望根治傷患<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7271095.stm |title=Operation ends Kightly's season |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-02-09 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307155445/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7271095.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，可望在季尾復出<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7303448.stm |title=Kightly could return within weeks |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-03-18 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307213708/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7303448.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月3日舉行的「2008年足球聯賽頒獎禮」（Football League Awards），禮利獲選「年度最佳青年球員」（Young Player of the Year）<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7267383.stm |title=Phillips wins Championship award |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-03-03 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2020-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626145708/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7267383.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月10日禮利在預備隊復出踢了半場比賽，雖然狀態未足，仍希望為球隊爭取升級附加賽席位盡一分力<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7340454.stm |title=Kightly on Wolves comeback trail |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-10 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307020639/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7340454.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月19日主場1-1賽和[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|葉士域治]]，禮利正式在一隊復出，於下半場後補上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7344112.stm |title=Wolves 1-1 Ipswich |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-19 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307161745/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7344112.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，4月22日主場對[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]，禮利正選上陣，下半場為球隊攻入最後一球以3-0大勝對手，保持一絲晉身附加賽的機會<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7356005.stm |title=Wolves 3-0 Cardiff |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-22 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307001414/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7356005.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，賽後獲領隊[[米克·麦卡锡|麦卡锡]]點名稱讚<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7362678.stm |title=Kightly's been immense - McCarthy |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-23 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307082103/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7362678.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；4月26日作客對[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]，狼隊半場落後0-1，下半場禮利在禁區內被侵犯獲判[[十二碼|十二碼]]，由[[西尔万·埃班克斯-布莱克|比歷克]]主罰入網扳平1-1完場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7356030.stm |title=Coventry 1-1 Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-26 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2018-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614101027/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7356030.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；5月4日聯賽煞科日主場僅能1-0小勝[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|普利茅夫]]，與[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]同分，以1球[[得失球差|得失球差]]不及而失落附加賽席位<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7368635.stm |title=Wolves 1-0 Plymouth |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-04 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2015-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150529070428/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7368635.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在這個被受傷患影響的球季，禮利僅上陣25場及射入5球。每到季後總有傳聞禮利將會跳槽，狼隊首席執行官莫可希（Jez Moxey）率先否認<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7433273.stm |title=No offers in for Kightly - Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-06-03 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307161131/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7433273.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，雖然言之鑿鑿禮利將會轉投[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]或[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]，領隊麦卡锡保證無人離隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7440190.stm |title=McCarthy says players will stay |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-06-06 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307043847/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7440190.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，6月24日禮利簽署四年新約結束一切的蜚短流長<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7471056.stm |title=Kightly pens new deal with Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-06-24 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506051544/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7471056.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2008年至2009年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2008/09年球季]]揭幕戰作客的對手正正是上季最後一戰的[[普利茅斯足球俱乐部|普利茅夫]]，禮利為狼隊射入本季首個入球扳平1-1，最終2-2和局完場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7540952.stm |title=Plymouth 2-2 Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-09 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2020-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630112636/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7540952.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月30日聯賽主場5-1大勝[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]，禮利梅開二度<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7578476.stm |title=Wolves 5-1 Nottm Forest |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-30 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806134743/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7578476.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，開季4場聯賽射入3球。禮利成為狼隊的當然正選，在9月30日主場0-3負於[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]感到腿筋刺痛而提早離場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7639348.stm |title=Wolves 0-3 Reading |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-09-30 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920033347/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7639348.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，初時恐怕要養傷1個月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7645696.stm |title=Wolves hamstrung without wingers |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-10-01 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2019-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816090901/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7645696.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，麦卡锡慌忙從[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]借用[[卡洛斯·爱德华兹|卡路士·艾華斯]]作為替補<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7648400.stm |title=Wolves complete Edwards loan deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-10-02 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2008-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081004123609/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7648400.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但僅缺陣1場即在10月18日對[[考文垂足球俱乐部|高雲地利]]及時復出<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7669916.stm |title=Kightly ready for Wolves return |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-10-14 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307021122/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7669916.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並射入一球協助球隊反勝2-1<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7665092.stm |title=Wolves 2-1 Coventry |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-10-18 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2020-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200131021546/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7665092.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月8日狼隊主場2-0擊敗[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|般尼]]，禮利包辦主隊兩個入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7698210.stm |title=Wolves 2-0 Burnley |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-11-08 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307073552/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7698210.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。禮利在新年前已射入7球，而狼隊亦在聯賽榜上獨佔鼇頭<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7775842.stm |title=Doncaster 0-1 Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-12-20 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310074641/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7775842.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，領隊麦卡锡再次強調不會在1月轉會窗將禮利出售<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7784062.stm |title=My stars not for sale - McCarthy |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-12-15 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307043435/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7784062.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年3月21日作客對[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]，已4個多月未有進賬的禮利於下半場一箭定江山<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7937220.stm |title=Nottm Forest 0-1 Wolves |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-21 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307212212/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7937220.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，為狼隊增添3分，聯賽尚餘六輪，在榜首領先次席的[[伯明翰城足球俱乐部|伯明翰城]]5分。3月31日禮利在一場無關重要對[[谢斯伯利足球俱乐部|梳士貝利]]的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]中受傷離場，賽後掃瞄證實左腳[[蹠骨|蹠骨]]骨折，將缺席球季餘下的比賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7975284.stm |title=Kightly's season ended by injury |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-01 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307130115/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7975284.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月18日狼隊聯賽主場1-0擊敗[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]後，提早兩輪確定直接升級[[英超|英超]]資格<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7990074.stm |title=Wolves 1-0 QPR |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-18 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2013-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130105073051/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/7990074.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，4月25日狼隊作客1-1賽和[[巴恩斯利足球俱乐部|班士利]]後確定贏得聯賽冠軍<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8001872.stm |title=Barnsley 1-1 Wolverhampton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-25 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2017-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827220527/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8001872.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。4月26日禮利入選[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|PFA]][[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]][[PFA年度最佳陣容|年度最佳陣容]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8019726.stm |title=Giggs earns prestigious PFA award |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-26 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2018-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616233508/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8019726.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

但禮利在[[英超|英超]]的首季仍然受到傷患困擾，直到2009年9月中才告康復，於0-0賽和[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:西汉姆联; zh-hk:韋斯咸;}-]]首次在英超亮相<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8259144.stm |title=Wolves boosted by Kightly return |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-09-16 |accessdate=2010-07-08 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307223843/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8259144.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在11月底對[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰城]]時又弄傷[[腳踝|腳踝]]，需要動[[手術|手術]]而缺陣8星期<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8389405.stm |title=Wolves winger Michael Kightly out for up to eight weeks |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-12-01 |accessdate=2010-07-08 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307085925/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8389405.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在腳踝傷患好轉時，其[[膝蓋|膝蓋]]又出問題，連續的傷患直到球季結束仍未復原，整季僅上陣10場。

2010年7月，禮利經歷漫長的復康治療，包括採用反重力跑步機（anti-gravity treadmill），終於可以重返球隊，前往[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]進行季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8796603.stm |title=Michael Kightly gives Wolves fitness boost |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-07-07 |accessdate=2010-07-08 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310125626/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8796603.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然未有獲得狼隊註冊入[[英超|英超]]25人參賽名單內，時任領隊[[米克·麥卡錫|米克·麥卡錫]]認為如禮利傷癒，可先行外借恢復狀態，於1月再重新加入大隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8963542.stm |title=Michael Kightly still has future with Wolves |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-09-02 |accessdate=2010-12-22 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307122522/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/8963542.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在腳踝痊癒後，禮利於10月26日遠赴[[瑞典|瑞典]]接受[[手術|手術]]治理右[[膝蓋|膝蓋]]的髕骨肌腱問題<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/9128335.stm |title=Wolves winger Michael Kightly to undergo knee surgery |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-10-26 |accessdate=2010-12-22 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310125638/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/9128335.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月21日禮利再上手術床，輪到左膝蓋接受與10月相同的手術<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/9309917.stm |title=Wolves winger Michael Kightly has second knee operation |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-21 |accessdate=2010-12-22 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307070731/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/9309917.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

過去兩季僅合共在[[英超|英超]]上陣13場，2011年7月18日尚餘一年合約在身的禮利獲狼隊延長多一年合約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14187370.stm |title=Wolves winger Michael Kightly signs contract extension |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-18 |accessdate=2011-07-19 |archive-date=2011-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110818082735/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14187370.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。10月11日於球季上陣5場後，禮利獲准外借到[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|屈福特]]，為期1個月以爭取更多上陣時間<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/15265177.stm |title=Watford sign Wolves winger Michael Kightly on loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-10-11 |accessdate=2011-10-12 |archive-date=2011-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111216040814/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/15265177.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。禮利逐漸恢復狀態，更於11月19日主場2-0勝[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:朴茨茅斯; zh-hk:樸茨茅夫;}-]]取得加盟後首球，隨即獲延長借用至翌年1月3日<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_7320976,00.html |title=Kightly extends Watford loan |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-11-20 |accessdate=2011-11-21 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308042135/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_7320976,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間合共上陣12場及射入3球。

;史篤城
於[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]降班[[英冠|英冠]]及僅餘一年合約，禮利在2012年8月8日以沒有透露的7位數字轉會費加盟[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]，合約的年期亦沒有透露<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19178586 |title=Michael Kightly: Stoke City sign Wolves winger |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-08-08 |accessdate=2012-08-19 |archive-date=2012-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120829105524/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19178586 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月18日英超開鑼日史篤城作客升班馬[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]，禮利於上半場為球隊首開記錄，最終各一言和收場<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19221348 |title=Reading 1-1 Stoke |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-08-18 |accessdate=2012-08-19 |archive-date=2012-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120819030104/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/19221348 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年9月2日，史篤城將27歲的禮利外借到[[英冠|英冠]]球會般尼一個球季<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23938853 |title=Stoke winger Michael Kightly in Burnley loan |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-09-02 |accessdate=2013-11-19 |archive-date=2014-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224234630/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/23938853 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 國家隊 ===
2007年8月16日禮利獲徵召加入[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]備戰對羅馬尼亞U21的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]，是8名新面孔之一<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6949403.stm |title=Agbonlahor in England U21 squad |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-08-16 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2017-08-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816112934/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6949403.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於8月21日首次披甲擔任正選踢了上半場的45分鐘<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6956354.stm |title=England U21 1-1 Romania U21 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-08-21 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201035730/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6956354.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月11日在[[2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]外圍賽作客出戰保加利亞U21，禮利下半場入替[[加布里埃尔·阿格邦拉霍|艾邦拉荷]]，英格蘭U21小勝2-0<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6988587.stm |title=Bulgaria U21 0-2 England U21 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-09-11 |accessdate=2009-05-20 |archive-date=2019-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701175728/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6988587.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008年2月尾禮利接受[[足踝|足踝]][[手術|手術]]後，缺席3月25日在[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]主場摩連納斯球場（Molineux stadium）對波蘭U21的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7305358.stm |title=Pearce excited by Fox and Dann |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-03-19 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307213246/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7305358.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然在球季末復出，但仍未百分百復原，於5月4日再次退出對威爾斯U21的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7401306.stm |title=Kightly pulls out of U21 friendly |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-14 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307140351/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7401306.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月19日主賽[[友誼賽|友賽]]斯洛文尼亞U21，禮利下半場入替[[詹姆斯·米尔纳|占士·米拿]]，有一次左腳射門中柱不入<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7571409.stm |title=England U21 2-1 Slovenia U21 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-19 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2017-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014235429/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7571409.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月5日主場2-0擊敗葡萄牙U21，英格蘭U21確保[[2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]附加賽的資格，禮利於完場前才後補上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7601429.stm |title=England U21 2-0 Portugal U21 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-09-05 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2017-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015045304/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7601429.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月18日主場[[友誼賽|友賽]]2-0擊敗捷克U21，禮利是四名踢足全場的球員之一<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7736671.stm |title=England U21 2-0 Czech Rep U21 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-11-18 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2008-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081219104114/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7736671.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。英格蘭U21教練[[斯图尔特·皮尔斯|皮雅斯]]在首次徵召禮利時，曾告訴他自己亦是由非聯賽球員身份扶搖直上，希望禮利能亦步亦趨，在他受傷期間亦經常來電查詢傷勢進展<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7735655.stm |title=Kightly flying high |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-11-21 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307072701/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7735655.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年2月10日英格蘭U21到[[西班牙|西班牙]][[馬拉加|馬拉加]]出戰[[厄瓜多爾國家足球隊|厄瓜多爾國家隊]]，禮利正選上陣，英格蘭小國腳上半場先入兩球，惟因經驗不足，於下半場倒輸三球而以2-3敗陣而回<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7882614.stm |title=Ecuador 3-2 England U21 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-02-10 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2009-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090213104605/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7882614.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。禮利在3月31日折斷左腳蹠骨而缺陣了整季賽事，他更會進行[[手術|手術]]治理其長久[[臀|臀部]][[屈肌|屈肌]]的傷患<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7979818.stm |title=McCarthy positive about Kightly |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-02 |accessdate=2009-05-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307053049/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/7979818.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，因而缺陣英格蘭U21在6月舉行的[[瑞典|瑞典]][[2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]決賽週比賽，而在此之後，他已超齡不會再代表英格蘭U21上陣。

